pageContext.course_type_long_description: Learn about Native American cultures and build your own totem pole out of LEGO® materials. Then work together to build the majestic Mayflower ship and journey across the ocean to celebrate the first Thanksgiving!
pageContext.course_type_name: The First Thanksgiving with LEGO® Materials
pageContext.action_url_comment: Registration is handled through the City of Shoreline online service.  It is also possible to register in person at Spartan Recreation Center.
